      "text": "Middleware chain (src/app.ts):\n  1. morgan(\"dev\")         → Log: POST /api/register 201\n  2. express.json()        → Parsea JSON body a req.body\n  3. sessionMiddleware     → express-session (store: connect-pg-simple → PostgreSQL tabla sessions)\n  4. routes                → Enruta al Router principal (src/routes.ts)",
